Dialogue: 5,0:23:55.87,0:24:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Guided by instinct, are we brought to\Na rift between humans and non-humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:58.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（チセ）\N本能の導く先にあるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:01.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは\N人と 人ならざる者の間に横たわる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:04.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,埋めようのない隔絶なのか
Dialogue: 5,0:24:01.96,0:24:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,one which we can never overcome?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:04.75,0:24:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are so foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.83,0:24:06.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リャナン･シー）人間って バカね
Dialogue: 5,0:24:06.84,0:24:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And selfish, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.12,0:24:09.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして わがままだわ
